選擇，後患無窮，大家可能要適當處理自己的資產！！同埋將五大訴求同經濟復甦掛勾，有左普選制度，香港係一個更公開，更公平既自治地方，大家就會有信心投資！大家唔好比緊急法嚇到，被政府帶風向，大家focus太多係蒙面法，私了，裝修，呢個緊急法既經濟炸彈大家要識得用！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f5ddfa83e4dfbfe5e4745e480abb82c3c01c07bd","tid":1633251,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:29:11.000Z","msg":"唔好咁多大字得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131f031fb3d09f67eefefb9aff4e022bbbfe133b","tid":1633251,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"有人好驚拉唔到人"},{"pid":"9cd21057969a39985fa91a5c91a59a2d64814b1a","tid":1633251,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80d3f0a80a237ab5b6c122045cf41b6e0305b1aa","tid":1633251,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:30:31.000Z","msg":"有人好急住要END GAME wor<br />\n我地大把時間可以慢慢撚你吹？<br />\n<br />\n《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoUIDL4SB60g&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4gNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=362ff721\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oUIDL4SB60g</a>"},{"pid":"0403692da43270a641a8e459b1bb0a7991ae8b71","tid":1633251,"uid":300136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:33:52.000Z","msg":"前線唔駛休息？你自己又唔出？為開花而開花？<br />\n利申612起次次星期6日都係前線"},{"pid":"895e63058de89d05226a52f7d33a95c84317f797","tid":1633251,"uid":27854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:46:00.000Z","msg":"聽日大把時間休啦，點解唔好好用埋呢個紅日？"},{"pid":"451cb3967e9f6acc0199b5e7cefa38330b4637b7","tid":1633251,"uid":52566,"like":0